<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<android.support.v4.widget.NestedScrollView xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    app:layout_behavior="@string/appbar_scrolling_view_behavior"
    tools:context="com.example.ada.smartcitadel.ScrollingActivity2"
    tools:showIn="@layout/activity_scrolling2">


    <LinearLayout
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:orientation="vertical">

        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_margin="3dp"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="match_parent"
            android:orientation="horizontal">

            <HorizontalScrollView
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="match_parent">

                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:orientation="horizontal">

                    <ImageView
                        android:id="@+id/imageView3"
                        android:layout_width="150dp"
                        android:layout_height="200dp"
                        android:layout_weight="1"
                        app:srcCompat="@drawable/poza1" />

                    <ImageView
                        android:id="@+id/imageView2"
                        android:layout_width="150dp"
                        android:layout_height="200dp"
                        android:layout_weight="1"
                        app:srcCompat="@drawable/poza" />

                    <ImageView
                        android:id="@+id/imageView"
                        android:layout_width="150dp"
                        android:layout_height="200dp"
                        app:srcCompat="@drawable/poza1" />

                    <ImageView
                        android:id="@+id/imageView4"
                        android:layout_width="150dp"
                        android:layout_height="200dp"
                        android:layout_weight="1"
                        app:srcCompat="@drawable/poza1" />

                </LinearLayout>

            </HorizontalScrollView>
        </LinearLayout>
        <TextView
            android:layout_marginTop="15dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="20dp"
            android:textAlignment="inherit"
            android:textSize="20sp"
            android:id="@+id/textView5"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:textColor="#000000"
            android:lineSpacingExtra="5dp"

            android:text="Poarta a II-a: O istorie zbuciumata
/n
Cu toate ca a fost demolata partial in anul 1937, poarta a II-a a fost reconstruita in anul 2009, pe baza elementelor originale pastrate (stalpii laterali, atlantii si un leu rampant) si pe baza unei imagini vechi. Intre cei doi stalpi incastrati in zidurile din caramida care marginesc barbacana se aflau, initial, doua volume de zidarie cu pilastri aplatizati in zona mediana. Pe cate un postament situat la baza acestora se inalta doi atlanti care sustin capiteluri cu volute, de factura ionica. Cate un leu rampant se afla pe fiecare dintre acestea, avand un scut cu emblema imparatului Carol al VI-lea." />


    </LinearLayout>
</android.support.v4.widget.NestedScrollView>
